Title: Directs the state liquor authority to extend all liquor licenses for on-premise alcohol retailers for a period of one year
Summary: Directs the state liquor authority to extend all liquor licenses for on-premise alcohol retailers for a period of one year at no cost to the licensee.
ActClause: AN ACT in relation to directing the state liquor authority to extend liquor licenses for on-premise alcohol retailers for a period of one year
